{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS Object Model","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS Object Model</strong>&nbsp;是一组允许用 JavaScript 操纵 CSS 的 API。 它是继 DOM 和 HTML API 之后，又一个操纵 CSS 的接口，从而能够动态地读取和修改 CSS 样式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"api参考","title":"API 参考","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect1\">\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>CSSCharsetRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSCounterStyleRule\"><code>CSSCounterStyleRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSFontFaceRule\"><code>CSSFontFaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>CSSFontFeatureValuesMap</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>CSSFontFeatureValuesRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSImportRule\"><code>CSSImportRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>CSSMarginRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStylesheet</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>CSSVariablesMap</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>CSSViewportRule</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/style\"><code>ElementCSSInlineStyle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>GeometryUtils</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>GetStyleUtils</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLLinkElement\"><code>LinkStyle</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaList\"><code>MediaList</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>PseudoElement</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>Stylesheet</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StylesheetList</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<p>CSSOM 相关规范也扩展了其他几个接口：</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLImageElement\"><code>HTMLImageElement</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a>, and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"教程","title":"教程","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model/Determining_the_dimensions_of_elements\">Determining the dimensions of elements</a> (这篇文档可能有点过时，因为它是在的 DHTML/Ajax 时代写的).</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model/Managing_screen_orientation\">Managing screen orientation</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spec-table standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">进度</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">评价</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/screen-orientation/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Screen Orientation API\" rel=\" noopener\">Screen Orientation API</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-fonts-3/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Fonts Module Level&nbsp;3\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Fonts Module Level&nbsp;3</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-animations-1/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Animations Level 1\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Animations Level 1</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-transitions/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Transitions\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Transitions</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-variables-1/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Custom Properties for Cascading Variables Module Level&nbsp;1\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Custom Properties for Cascading Variables Module Level&nbsp;1</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-3/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Conditional Rules Module Level&nbsp;3\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Conditional Rules Module Level&nbsp;3</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-device-adapt/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Device Adaptation\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Device Adaptation</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-counter-styles-3/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Counter Styles Level&nbsp;3\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Counter Styles Level&nbsp;3</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"浏览器兼容性","title":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>近几年所有的这些新特性正在一点一点的向不同的浏览器内添加，不过这确实是一个很复杂无法用简单表格总结的过程。如果具体项目中需要用到，请详细的检查接口的可用性。</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"API 参考","id":"api参考"},{"text":"教程","id":"教程"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"CSS Object Model 是一组允许用 JavaScript 操纵 CSS 的 API。 它是继 DOM 和 HTML API 之后，又一个操纵 CSS 的接口，从而能够动态地读取和修改 CSS 样式。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS Object Model","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"CSS Object Model","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS オブジェクトモデル (CSSOM)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSS 객체 모델 (CSSOM)","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"CSS Object Model","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSS Object Model","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/css_object_mode